A plugin that adds a qrcode-function to Prawn::Document


======= Dependencies ========
* Prawn
* RQRCode

======= Usage =======
In your pdf, do:
pdf.qrcode(@qrcode) 
and your qrcode will be drawn in the pdf.

====== Documentation =======
Prawn::Document::qrcode(qrcode,xpos=0,ypos=0,module_size=4,module_factor=1.1)

qrcode:
	An object of the module RQRCode

xpos, ypos:
	Relative movements. The xpos is relative from a centered position. Please note that increasing the ypos moves the qrcode upwards (this is because of prawn)

module_size:
	The size of the black and white blocks in the qrcode

module_factor: 
	The size of the drawn blocks (the black ones) are multiplied with this factor.

